Tests list
==========

Greetings generator
-------------------

* one employee, create greetings (OK)

* one employee, do not create greetings

* multiple employees, create greetings for them

* multiple employees, do not create greetings for them

* employeeDataMissing or I/O exception, do not create greetings


CheckForBirthday
----------------

* todayIsBirthdayOfEmployee

* todayIsNOTBirthdayOfEmployee

